tweet: May all nations serve Thee, O Lord.  In Whom are all created things in heaven and on earth, visible and invisible,
May all nations serve Thee, O Lord.  Who art throned and crowned at the right hand of Thy Father,
May all nations serve Thee, O Lord.  Who in Thy glorified body art risen triumphant,
May all nations serve Thee, O Lord.  Who in Thy Resurrection wert the First-born from the dead,
May all nations serve Thee, O Lord.  Who didst ransom Thy people by the royal Sacrifice of Calvary,
